WEBVTT

00:07.780 --> 00:10.615
If you guys stumbled across some ooze,

00:10.617 --> 00:14.619
would you guys, you know, ingest it
or roll around in it to gain powers

00:14.621 --> 00:15.953
like the Teenage Mutant
Ninja Turtles did?

00:15.955 --> 00:18.856
Did the Turtles eat it, or did
they just happen to wallow in it?

00:18.858 --> 00:20.558
- They wallowed.
- Yeah.

00:20.560 --> 00:22.960
All right, well, exactly what
room do we find this ooze in?

00:22.962 --> 00:25.296
[all laugh]

00:25.298 --> 00:26.464
I mean, I'll give it a shot.

00:26.466 --> 00:28.032
Daredevil, turned out okay for him.

00:28.034 --> 00:29.667
The Turtles, turned out okay for them.

00:29.669 --> 00:31.836
Even Toxic Avenger's well-respected.

00:31.838 --> 00:32.970
Yeah.

00:32.972 --> 00:34.338
Who did it not turn out okay for?

00:34.340 --> 00:36.307
Nobody. I mean, the ooze could be better

00:36.309 --> 00:38.142
than what's going, what,
you know, our existence

00:38.144 --> 00:39.911
right now, for some of us, right?

00:39.913 --> 00:41.812
I'm saying it's
definitely gonna be better.

00:41.814 --> 00:44.248
[all laugh]

